name: Anger with the world
description:
Woman Portrait Original Photo By Sean Jahansooz 
 
About Artist:
Shahram Jahansooz Iranian Photographer based in Toronto-Dubai is a member of several photography institutes and associations such as the Iranian Photography Center, The International Federation of Photographic Art (FIAP), Germany's GNS international association and the International Association of Press Photography (IAPP). He started his professional career as a cinema and television photographer and has had many photography exhibitions in and outside of Iran.[1][2] He started his career in 2001 with cinematography, portrait and nature photography, he has had 2 solo exhibitions in different galleries in Iran [2][3][4] and Mexico[5] and his works have been elected in many photo festivals around the world such as Iran,[6][7] Spain, Croatia, England, United States[8] and Montenegro.[9]
